The National Convention for Construction and Reform – Mageuzi (NCCR-Mageuzi) Presidential candidate Jeremiah Maganja has congratulated the National Electoral Commission (NEC) for a well organised election. Speaking to reporters on Wednesday (October 28, 2020) in Bunda, Mara shortly after casting his ballot, the candidate said the exercise has been handled professionally. “Since Tanzania conducted its first multiparty election in 1995 after reintroduction of the system in 1992, this exercise is being conducted very professionally,” he said